<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  {{> head title=title}}
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 antialiased">
  {{> toast}}

  <main class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute left-[-100px] top-[-90px] h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-primary-200/70 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[-120px] right-[-120px] h-[26rem] w-[26rem] rounded-full bg-sky-200/70 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(248,250,252,0.95),rgba(255,255,255,0.88))]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid min-h-screen lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]">
      <section class="relative hidden overflow-hidden bg-[linear-gradient(160deg,#1d4ed8_0%,#2563eb_35%,#0f766e_100%)] text-white lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-between">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
          <div class="absolute left-12 top-20 h-32 w-32 rounded-full border border-white/30"></div>
          <div class="absolute right-16 top-40 h-20 w-20 rounded-full border border-white/30"></div>
          <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-24 h-44 w-44 rounded-full border border-white/20"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(255,255,255,0.18),transparent_30%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.14),transparent_25%)]"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 p-12">
          {{> auth-brand}}
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 px-12">
          <div class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-50 backdrop-blur">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
            Secure Access Experience
          </div>

          <h1 class="max-w-xl text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight xl:text-5xl">
            Quản lý đăng nhập, bảo mật và truy cập hệ thống mượt mà hơn.
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-primary-100">
            Khu vực auth được tách riêng để tối ưu trải nghiệm đăng nhập, đăng ký,
            khôi phục mật khẩu và kiểm soát truy cập rõ ràng hơn cho cả admin lẫn user.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-10 grid max-w-xl gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/10 p-5 backdrop-blur">
              <div class="mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white/15">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-lock"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xl font-black">JWT</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-primary-100">Xác thực</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/10 p-5 backdrop-blur">
              <div class="mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white/15">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xl font-black">MVC</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-primary-100">HBS Views</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white/10 p-5 backdrop-blur">
              <div class="mb-3 flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white/15">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xl font-black">Access</p>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-primary-100">Phân quyền</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between p-12 text-sm text-primary-100">
          <p>© 2026 NestJS HBS Project</p>
          <a href="/" class="font-semibold text-white hover:text-primary-100">
            Về trang chủ
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center px-5 py-10 sm:px-8">
        <div class="w-full max-w-md">
          <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center lg:hidden">
            {{> auth-brand}}
          </div>

          {{{body}}}

          <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xs font-medium text-slate-400">
            NestJS + HBS + Tailwind CSS + Flowbite
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  {{> scripts}}
</body>
</html>
